item.title: [508]Run Error -can't find patch- [508] Need help NOW
item.dc:creator: @elascape elascape
item.description:
@elascape wrote:

go to your c:/ files and into your program files and find your JRE type (mines jre 6) after you’ve found that go to “edit” on the run file and change where it says
"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk 6(whatever is here)\bin\java.exe

to

"C:\Program Files\Java\jre(whatever jre you have)\bin\java.exe

and then save it and it should work.
